# Ball Shooter — stable v2

`orbit-blast` is tagged `stable: 'v2'` in `src/platform/catalog.ts`. See `STABLE.md`.

## Do not change

Unless the user **explicitly authorizes** changes to Ball Shooter:

- Do not edit files under `src/games/orbit-blast/` or `games/orbit-blast/`
- Do not change ball shooting mechanics, ball physics, collision logic, level progression, difficulty, target spawning, or game rules
- Do not change backend or tournament integration
- Do not change premium presentation (UI, graphics, audio, effects, HUD, menus) without authorization

## Frozen scope

- `src/games/orbit-blast/game.ts` — gameplay + canvas rendering
- `src/games/orbit-blast/main.ts` — bootstrap, HUD wiring
- `src/games/orbit-blast/obAudio.ts` — premium SFX and music
- `src/games/orbit-blast/style.css` — Ethio Telecom premium theme
- `games/orbit-blast/index.html` — menus, HUD, overlays

## Instead

- Copy Ball Shooter **patterns** into shared modules or other games
- Fix platform/hub/backend issues without touching Ball Shooter game code
- If a shared change affects Ball Shooter, **tell the user** which shared file changed and why
